('6801163a2a03480', 'Poonam Astrotarot', 45, 'Female', '1745088085_img.png', '', '', 0, '2025-04-17 20:24:50', 'Online', '', 'English,Hindi', 'marital-life,love-relationship,career-job,cheating-affairs,numerology,vedic-astrology', 27, 12193, 5, 'poonam_astrotarot', '23', 'poonam@gmail.com', '9898989898', '&lt;p&gt;I have been practicing as an Astrology consultant for more than 2 decades now. I am also doing research in finance &amp;amp; market trends because business and career astrology is my passion. My readings are not sugar-coated and I always guide my clients with the truth. If you are trying to find the right path to build a happy and successful life with the help of planets and their influence on different aspects of your life, then approach me. I will help you discover new possibilities based on Astrological calculations and methods. Hindu Astrology includes several nuanced sub-systems of interpretation and prediction with elements and I am well acquainted with modern approaches in Vedic Hindu astrology. I am a very spiritual person, serving as an intuitive astrologer and counselor. I utilize my gift of clairvoyance in my readings and also guide people with the help of Astrology, Vastu, and Tarot. During the years of practice, I have studied in detail about Vedic Astrology and other major branches of Astrology like Parashar, Jaimini, Tajik, Western Astrology, Krishnamurthi, Nadi Lal Kitab, political astrology as well as Numerology, Tarot, Vastu, and Tantra. I will use my knowledge and inner calling to help you find the meaning of life.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;I am a certified Astrologer. My area of expertise lies in Parashar, Jaimini, Tajik, Western Astrology, Krishnamurthi, Nadi Lal Kitab, political astrology as well as Numerology, Tarot, Vastu, and Tantra. Based on my knowledge and research over the last 2 decades I am offering services in Astrology and suggesting solutions to my client to solve their problems in love &amp;amp; relationship, business &amp;amp; career, financial issues, marital life and breakups &amp;amp; divorce by analyzing their Horoscopes to understand the current and upcoming Karmic planetary influence on their life.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', '12345', '$6$rounds=5000$anexamplestringf$r1RDHXB89qVB/JMXSBxKbWyHqDlXk5vEuel7M4t3VtogexduEGucI.rt7XI1/bqaza5/Sv9bz/wIFCnIgCsHQ/', '2025-04-20', 0),
('68054cc3bcde846', 'LakhanJ', 22, 'Male', '1745177795_img.png', '17451777950_img.png,17451777951_img.png', '', 0, '2025-04-21 01:06:35', 'Online', '', 'English,Hindi', 'marital-life,love-relationship,career-job,cheating-affairs,breakup-divorce,vedic-astrology', 48, 6084, 5, 'lakhanj', '21', 'test@gmail.com', '9898989898', '&lt;p&gt;I provide Astrology services based on over a decade of experience. My expertise lies in various branches like Vedic Kundli, Lal Kitab, Vastu, and Tantra-Mantra. Through these, I offer detailed insights into life events, career paths, relationships, and remedies for prevailing issues. My consultations aim to bring clarity and guidance, helping individuals make informed decisions about their future. Whether it&#039;s analyzing birth charts, recommending remedies, or suggesting Vastu adjustments for harmonious living spaces, my services cater to diverse needs. I prioritize personalized attention, ensuring clients feel supported and empowered to navigate life&#039;s challenges with a clearer understanding.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;I have dedicated a decade to mastering Astrology, having honed my skills at Ved Vidyalaya in District Chittor. My qualifications include comprehensive knowledge of Vedic Kundli, Lal Kitab, Vastu principles, and Tantra-Mantra practices. Over the years, I&#039;ve assisted numerous individuals in decoding the complexities of their lives through Astrological insights. My experience extends beyond mere calculations; it encompasses a deep understanding of astrological nuances, allowing me to provide practical and effective solutions. Through continuous learning and application, I have refined my abilities to offer holistic guidance that aligns with individual needs, making a positive impact on the lives of those I assist.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '0000-00-00', 0),
