('68054e0a9dc8e50', 'GulshanA', 39, 'Male', '1745178122_img.png', '', '', 0, '2025-04-21 01:12:02', 'Online', '', 'English,Hindi,Sanskrit,Gujarati', 'cheating-affairs,numerology,breakup-divorce,vedic-astrology,kids-education,relationship-counseling', 48, 5456, 5, 'gulshana', '8', 'test@gmail.com', '9898989898', '&lt;p&gt;I am an expert in Vedic Astrology holding an experience of 5 years. I have done a certification course in Astrology from Jyotish Vidyapeeth. I can help you to take the right decisions regarding your personal as well as professional life with my knowledge of divine science.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;I am a professional Vedic Astrologer having 5 years of experience. I have completed my B.A in Shastri from Rashtriya Sanskrit Sansthan. I have been certified in Vedic Astrology by Jyotish Vidyapeeth.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', '', '0000-00-00', 0),
('68054e425771870', 'RaviShankar', 37, 'Male', '1745178178_img.png', '', '', 0, '2025-04-21 01:12:58', 'Online', '', 'English,Hindi', 'career-job,cheating-affairs,numerology,breakup-divorce,vedic-astrology,kids-education,tarot-reading', 28, 5814, 5, 'ravishankar', '26', 'test@gmail.com', '9898989898', '&lt;p&gt;I am an Astrology expert with knowledge in Vedic and KP Astrology as well as Palmistry, gained through dedicated learning. My aim is to provide guidance in various life aspects. I offer consultations to aid in matters such as careers, finance, marriage, education, children, and legal issues. I believe in simple yet effective remedies that can positively impact life. My approach is to provide practical solutions to enhance well-being, using the insights gained from Astrology and Palmistry. I strive to offer clear and understandable advice, tailored to each individual&#039;s needs, aiming to bring positivity and solutions to their lives. I specialize in providing personalized consultations that delve into the depths of Vedic and KP Astrology alongside Palmistry. Through these ancient sciences, I offer insights and guidance tailored to your unique life circumstances. My approach emphasizes clarity and simplicity, ensuring that the remedies and advice I provide are easy to understand and implement. I am committed to empowering individuals to navigate life&#039;s challenges with confidence and positivity, using the wisdom of Astrology to illuminate their path towards fulfillment and happiness.&amp;lt;/p&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;My journey in Astrology began with a solid foundationu2014a graduation in commerce and an MBA in finance, providing a comprehensive understanding of financial matters. Additionally, I pursued extensive learning in Vedic and KP Astrology, as well as Palmistry, under the guidance of my respected Guruji. With years of dedicated study and practical application, I have honed my skills to provide accurate and insightful guidance. My experien